data.description: Just listed! Beautiful home, original owners. Start by taking in the beautiful and mature landscaping before you enter the foyer of this immaculate 4 bedroom and 3 1/2 bath split level home and make your way a few steps up into the huge family room. Fabulous deep and rich original hardwood floors and a stone fireplace immediately grab your attention. The room is open and airy. The spacious, fully-equipped, and open kitchen is adjacent to the family room and has warm cr me tile flooring. The countertops are butcherblock with tile backsplashes. The gas stove is ready to immediately bring out the smells of cooking.                            The three upstairs bedrooms are spacious and have the same deep and rich hardwood floors as the family room. Closet space abounds throughout. The bathrooms are tiled, spacious and most attractive with custom sinks and mirrors. The over-sized all-tiled basement has a large suite and is fully equipped and ready for those special family members or friends. Step through the back doors onto the huge wooden deck overlooking the shady, fenced back yard. A fabulous area to entertain loved ones and old friends. Or you can walk out from the basement into a beautiful, well-manicured garden area featuring an attractive water feature. There is no HOA. You can indulge in the convenience of upscale shopping in the historic town of Villa Rica, while the picturesque landscapes of the north Georgia mountains beckon for exploration. A short drive puts you into close proximity to all that Marietta has to offer, including hospitals, shopping, and renowned restaurants. For jet setting off to your favorite destinations, ATL is also quite convenient. This beautiful and quiet property epitomizes refined living in a desirable location. Don't let this extraordinary opportunity slip through your grasp!
